bodyText: My name is Tyler, and diligent software engineer with 5+ years of experience in commercial applications and software development. Eager to build innovative and cutting-edge technologies focusing on full-stack experience with the specialization on backend web development. I have a bachelors degree in Computer Science and am skilled in a variety of programming languages including PL/SQL, JavaScript, and C#. Throughout my career I worked on a variety of projects from small personal web applications to large-scale enterprise systems. I am particularly interested in developing applications for the web and mobile platform. I am a dedicated and passionate software developer, constantly seeking to improve my skills and stay up-to-date with the latest industry trends. Please feel free to contact with me to learn more about my work and experience.
